Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\c&H87F8FF&\pos(1160,676)}四月28日 Eternidate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說過了你應該休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不肯聽別人的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發熱是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不一樣 我一直是個hot的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉好奇怪 好hot啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月28日 Michiko病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煉獄108度電波
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(150,50)\pos(1145,658)}四月29日 日出飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你母親生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你母親吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多大了？ 10歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過長大后就會變得扭曲、丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是會那樣的孩子 真羨慕你母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做旅行是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實阿姨我也是旅行者 雖然是獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的要困難很多啊 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吧 真的是很孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 水龍頭不可以一直開著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 有事情的話可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃藥的話要花多少天才會好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖的越久住宿費越多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 只有逃跑了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊的話有花27Arca就可住下的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我可以做的工作 我什么都愿意干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這個號碼打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個簡單的工作 收入也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 沒有身份證也可以去的醫院有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話不要太貴 但是醫術高明的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決對不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞得像個小孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的話 能治好的病也好不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病已經好了 精神十足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去你一個人去 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太孩子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配這個宇宙的法則你們知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是原因和結果的因果律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是能夠打破因果律的唯一的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人們稱我為Deus(葡語：神)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神親自操刀的話 什么病都會瞬間消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去 但是我只能找到這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備手術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿意度120% 奇跡般的Show Time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想對我注射這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們坐超特快列車下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是普通的麻醉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson 給我按好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是無 無的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang（宇宙誕生的大爆炸）!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴張的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒照亮黑暗的銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太陽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開天辟地！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼霧喚雨 化為海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地出現 動物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我創造了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿是缺陷的失敗之作 你聽的到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生命的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫生好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是一切的元兇 你可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是神技 Magic Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是病歷和賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 和之前說的價格不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附加治療 另外付費？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那么多錢 而且事前我也沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在你聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能這樣... 我無法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑Deus我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幸福的傳道士 一次都沒有覺得自己是神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次都沒有過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amigo(葡語：朋友)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是的你Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這個份上你還不相信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的努力就付諸東流了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家伙的病也永遠不會好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢的話 我今晚會去打工 明天一定付
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信Deus了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的承諾要用書面形式記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像坐超特快列車下地獄的只有我一個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死嗎 臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼在看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\c&HBED0F0&\pos(1172,706)}荒野農場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的山賊來了的話 就大聲呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 別讓他們逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以借用電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(250,0)\c&H4EBAF7&\pos(1152,688)}四月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意志還比不上狗啊 錢不能給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你想拿多少就拿多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 Bud
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 明天 明天是不會平等地出現在每個人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在規定日期內未能支付費用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每超過1日 作為利息收取雙倍費用 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有寫過這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是你寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的字才沒有這么難看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去警察局嗎 Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂 求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盤問起來的話 就不只是一點小問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒一點沒有退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么要喝這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喉嚨痛 喝一點會舒服些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以喝了一點點...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 我聽不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喝這種東西 病才沒有好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白！ 完全不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我虛弱的時候 對我溫柔點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然賣相不好 不過看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我有個請求...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺什么事情都會順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Hiroshi啊 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山賊們今晚會來 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晰的第六感是這樣告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你女兒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是某人要的氣味樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這個是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feliciano剛剛被人甩了 完全地受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會走掉的 Feliciano
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個女博士歡好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女...博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的葡萄酒很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭生啤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}注：暗示不帶安全套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的 你一定會沉迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒點風險也值得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個適合我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜看我內褲的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭被束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和服穿起來松松的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從和你相識開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想過 說不定你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 Hiroshi 我現在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭生啤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的 你一定會沉迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開 我好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會走掉的 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個女博士歡好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么... 回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些家伙對我下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于墮落成山賊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投無路了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有帶你的母親去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 去了一個叫Deus的人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 那個家伙不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮上沒有人不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先是地下醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后來為了還賭債才開始搞那個心靈手術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈手術？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不用手術刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成從體內取出病巢的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實什么也不是 三流的魔術表演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把事先藏好的東西給人看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的口頭禪 “不愧是神技 Magic Hand”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人搭理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我是傻瓜 大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是神的話 我就要化為惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先給我跪下 Deus！ 談事情在這之后！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus！ 給我滾出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開對我下的詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下詛咒的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是詛咒 詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你和他們串通起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手里的鐵棒是怎么回事 想揍我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我才不怕你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球在運動 世界在轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前的行為非常野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(200,0)\c&H98D1E3&\pos(1156,692)}四月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還是去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天隔壁的阿姨會帶我們去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 被砸壞的電視機是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\pos(1157,687)}待續
